{"tid":1466681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］點樣可以做到唔畀鬼分化到？","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:37.000Z","uid":181050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9192502dfcaeeb2c733ae376393978d9fdd280f9","tid":1466681,"uid":181050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申：核彈定錫春袋都唔割</span></span><br />\n<br />\n眼見今日機場嘅好鬼<br />\n捉咗環球嗰記者之後<br />\n係咁叫「我叫斬佢中指 」行私刑咁款<br />\n又屌first aid又屌記者<br />\n唔多似平時手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">鬼就一定有兼捉唔晒<br />\n但點樣可以破解啲鬼帶動現場情緒同點樣唔好畀佢哋分化？</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n預咗畀人屌喺和理非同道德高地<br />\n但真心想集思廣益點想去破解"},{"pid":"03fd782d699b9e54415cabbbc5c0ccb891f83bd3","tid":1466681,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face